{"tid":584040,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"已經兩日無聯絡 病左都唔想博你同情","createTime":"2018-03-07T13:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T15:43:36.000Z","uid":153790,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"161f96bc85356a12474882c9bef1e5c5bf1bf83a","tid":584040,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"三日無同另一半聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但明明無鬧交 無嘈無性<br />\n都可以好似冷戰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 今日病到七彩 屋企又無人<br />\n我都無搵你 唔想博你同情 <br />\n自己死頂落街買粥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似邊個搵對方先就輸左咁<br />\n點解我地關係變成咁<br />\n我好辛苦 好想同你分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想搵一個愛我既人<br />\n唔係口講最愛 但扮愛我既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153b041cf4b97772496420af4a0d7c386a8e058b","tid":584040,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:27:06.000Z","msg":"好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊三年幾咁對我"},{"pid":"3d12d55fdcc18d192f6516f92e5d3125a3d5fddf","tid":584040,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:28:36.000Z","msg":"即使一個自愛也好　越對我好　越需要控制我反應<br />\n對未來還沒信心　怎張開眼睛<br />\n花花世界太過美　哪有我蹤影<br />\n有更心跳選擇　而比我遠遠優勝　如何專一都想轉性<br />\n<br />\n與情人齊眉白髮　問誰可保證"},{"pid":"78faa762292cf29d8ab5e4e709d2bbdfc2ffb76e","tid":584040,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d12d55fdcc18d192f6516f92e5d3125a3d5fddf","tid":584040,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:28:36.000Z","msg":"即使一個自愛也好　越對我好　越需要控制我反應<br />\n對未來還沒信心　怎張開眼睛<br />\n花花世界太過美　哪有我蹤影<br />\n有更心跳選擇　而比我遠遠優勝　如何專一都想轉性<br />\n<br />\n與情人齊眉白髮　問誰可保證"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 座右銘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki